data.description: Every square foot is maximized! This 4-bedroom home offers space, flexibility and comfort. Entering your new home, you are met with a foyer leading to your secluded study room. Opt to transform the study room into your office, gym or fifth bedroom!  The open-concept, two-story family room adjoined by the oversized kitchen & breakfast area is the heart of the home & full of natural light. The kitchen accommodates granite countertops, flat-panel birch cabinets, recess lighting, SS appliances as well as a kitchen island! The first floor holds your private primary suite with an elegant ensuite bathroom. The bathroom holds marble countertops with dual vanities, a shower/bathtub enclosure, and an expansive walk-in closet! Roam up the stairs to the second floor which is filled with three additional bedrooms, two full bathrooms and an oversized game room perfect for game nights with the family. Enjoy and Relax in the front porch or back patio. There's something for the entire family to enjoy!
